updateZOrder

public void updateZOrder(int minIndex,
                         int lastPaintIndex)
Modify paint order. Component with lastPaintIndex should be painted on top.

Parameters:
minIndex - Minimum index which can be used to update ZOrder - index is related to Container#getComponents(), minIndex is useful to preserve index values for additional components which should be painted on top
lastPaintIndex - Index of last painted component - index is related to OverlapBoxLayout#getComponents()
